data.description: Stunning doublewide mobile home with an addition on two lots on serene Church Lake. Impeccably maintained, boasting a newer metal roof, upgraded HVAC, and hot water heater. Relish mesmerizing sunsets from your private lakeside screened porch. Inside, discover a fully remodeled kitchen and an expansive owner's bath addition, creating a true oasis. This property offers more than just a beautiful home; it comes with a garage, RV parking,  carport,  office building, boat launch,  and even a private dock for your lakeside adventures. The office building would make wonderful sleeping quarters for overflow guests.  Don't let this incredible opportunity slip away!
